name: Selman Ercan's GitHub projects
body:
### Projects: * [GA](https://github.com/S-Ercan/GA)
Applying genetic programming to MAX-3SAT. * [QLearning](https://github.com/S-Ercan/QLearning)
Reinforcement learning agent learning to navigate a maze containing rewards and punishments using the Q-learning technique. * [dota2-deathmap](https://github.com/S-Ercan/dota2-deathmap)
Interactive D3 visualizations for a generated DotA 2 death map. * [PhiVis](https://github.com/S-Ercan/PhiVis)
Interactive D3 visualizations for the PHI-base data set.
